question: Question: This series is narrated by Nick Jenkins, while its other characters include Charles Stringham and Kenneth Widmerpool. For 10 points each: [10] Name this series of twelve novels depicting societal tensions in mid-20th-century England. Its first volume is A Question of Upbringing.
